Content: Doing a test run on a new creative. Inmates vs officers. Inmates_ can you run the prison? You got what it takes to pull off an escape? Officers can you keep your facility under control? Looking for atleast 15 players. DM if interested.

Prison wars. Inmates vs Officers. Scattered loot. Remote explosives. Inside and outside battlegrounds. Open and closed quarters. Sniper tower. Roof access to all. Minimum 4v4. All skill levels_ all teams welcomed. First test run was a blast! No escapes. Who’s got what it takes? NLDm me for more info. Thanks
